data.description: Well maintained home, this residence showcases a stunning living space and an expansive kitchen. The main house features three bedrooms and three bathrooms, including a bonus room perfect for various uses. There is an additional living space with two bedrooms and one bathroom, offering extra versatility. Enjoy the inviting Florida room, and discover the potential within the large workshop, currently utilized as a sawmill. In addition, the property is equipped with solar panels and a water system, emphasizing its commitment to sustainability. Completing the picture, there is a dedicated office space, underlining the home's functionality. Conveniently located near shopping and restaurants, this home is a testament to both comfort and versatility.
